  "text": "The present study sought to validate the Brazilian version of HOS (HOS-Brazil) using a group of physically active patients diagnosed with femoroacetabular impingement (FAI) or greater trochanteric pain syndrome (GTPS). This validated questionnaire will provide doctors and other healthcare providers in Brazil with a more specific instrument to assess this population of patients. Importantly, the hip research group at Pedro Ernesto University Hospital, State University of Rio de Janeiro (Hospital Universitário Pedro Ernesto, Universidade do Estado do Rio de Janeiro; HUPE/ UERJ) previously translated and culturally adapted the HOS [CITATION_1] .",
